name: xmas cult
description: XMAS is a full community takeover project on the Solana blockchain created after the original developer rugged the token. The community rebuilt the project with transparent ownership a doxxed lead team and open traceable wallets. XMAS aims to restore trust and deliver a fair Christmas themed meme coin powered by its holders. The project focuses on transparency sustainable growth and long term community engagement. Creator fees and revenue are reinvested to support development liquidity and visibility while all operations remain fully public. XMAS represents a fresh start and a committed effort to build a resilient and entertaining community driven token.
